    "These results indicated that the main CC market was inefficient.",
    "By employing a battery of efficiency tests and the Multifractal Detrended Fluctuation Analysis (MF-DFA) and Multifractal Detrended Cross-Correlation Analysis (MF-DCCA) approaches, Zhang et al. (2018) illustrate that the nine most popular CC markets were inefficient.",
